'''圣爱之母朝圣所'''（{{lang-it|Santuario della Madonna del Divino Amore}}）是意大利罗马的一座[[罗马天主教|罗马天主教]]朝圣所，供奉[[圣母玛利亚|圣母玛利亚]]。它包括两座教堂：老堂建于1745年，新堂建于1999年。2000年[[圣年|圣年]]期间，[[教宗若望保祿二世|教宗若望保祿二世]]将该堂列为[[罗马朝圣七大殿|罗马朝圣七大殿]]之一<ref>{{cite book| title = An American Story| first = Tony| last = Kim| publisher = Dorrance Publishing| url = https://books.google.com.br/books?id=A51qCcZh5yMC&lpg=PA10&ots=zKkOBU9Cli&dq=%22Santuario%20della%20Madonna%20del%20Divino%20Amore%22%20pope%202000%20Great%20Jubilee&hl=pt-BR&pg=PA10#v=onepage&q=%22Santuario%20della%20Madonna%20del%20Divino%20Amore%22%20pope%202000%20Great%20Jubilee&f=false| access-date = 2016-09-04| archive-date = 2016-08-10| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160810131809/https://books.google.com.br/books?id=A51qCcZh5yMC&lpg=PA10&ots=zKkOBU9Cli&dq=%22Santuario%20della%20Madonna%20del%20Divino%20Amore%22%20pope%202000%20Great%20Jubilee&hl=pt-BR&pg=PA10#v=onepage&q=%22Santuario%20della%20Madonna%20del%20Divino%20Amore%22%20pope%202000%20Great%20Jubilee&f=false| dead-url = no}}</ref>。
